riod of AU Mic b. The\npower of this emission (a few 10$^{17}$ W) is consistent with 3D\nmagnetohydrodynamical simulations of the interaction between stellar wind and\nthe close-in planet if the latter hosts a magnetic field of $\\sim$10 G.\nSpectropolarimetric observations of the star are needed to firmly elucidate the\norigin of the observed chromospheric variability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Mar 2022 18:39:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-24"}
