ive to each of the\nmentioned theoretical uncertainties, with a particular sensitivity to bulk\nviscosity, indicating that the latter is an important ingredient for an\naccurate treatment of deuteron production.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Mar 2022 22:05:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-14"}
