endors will\nbe necessary to improve mechanical properties and fabrication processes in\norder to produce hundreds of meters of fiber and instrument a large number of\naccelerator superconducting magnets. Those R&D efforts will last up to 10 years\nwith a founding level that spans between 5-10 M$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Mar 2022 23:00:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-17"}
